{"tid":2409712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁子超；新春聚會衍生的傳播源或於未來數天出現，復工復課時或有反彈","createTime":"2021-02-16T04:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:46:33.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb84dec674e4d7bf8e00b37d273b49c9269215b","tid":2409712,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情似有回落，昨日(15日)僅錄得9宗確診個案，宗數屬11月中以來最低。呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超認為只屬短暫現象，新春聚會衍生的傳播源或於未來數天出現，疫情仍隱憂，復工復課時或有反彈。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超今日(16日)接受港台《千禧年代》訪問時解釋，近日本港確診個案下跌，由年初一錄得源頭不明個案9宗，急跌至昨日2、3宗，相信只屬短暫現象，農曆新年聚會衍生的傳播源或於未來數天出現。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，近日預約檢測服務爆滿，或令有病徵或高風險因素的市民未能盡早檢測，<span class=\"red\">在復工復課後疫情有機會反彈，疫情仍存在隱憂。</span>"},{"pid":"b83b2ca92350732b90c1d598692ac27ca56d6c00","tid":2409712,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"咁永遠lockdown 一定最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bf0be1ef9e1a4f76cdaf1051981ab7d06b4252","tid":2409712,"uid":33522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"復工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四第五波有幾多公司真係有停過工"},{"pid":"7664ee9d9f9e45c4e46d562ef365c5c8a7ccdef8","tid":2409712,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:20:08.000Z","msg":"新春聚會會衍生傳播但係返工唔會, 都係返工安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c10d4f8211c81d4b8cfac24ef3e8b1b813e2ee","tid":2409712,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"病毒話搵工ga人有無敵抗體 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d950b39af18e0ada2778ed88ea466e9c5bd6ec","tid":2409712,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40bf0be1ef9e1a4f76cdaf1051981ab7d06b4252","tid":2409712,"uid":33522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"復工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四第五波有幾多公司真係有停過工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"究竟邊到停工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9277736e880ce6031a3a4fdb0cf69278e14b956","tid":2409712,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">黎字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"db92dc84cc5afc3dcc25e048576d02752460fc82","tid":2409712,"uid":197857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40bf0be1ef9e1a4f76cdaf1051981ab7d06b4252","tid":2409712,"uid":33522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"復工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四第五波有幾多公司真係有停過工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"政府自己囉 <br />\nd wfh 根本唔洗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6715088b8a684bfdc2692583612512a8130d2901","tid":2409712,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"以前覺得做醫生好叻<br />\n<br />\n而家真心覺得佢地離地加讀死書<br />\n<br />\n講野冇邏輯 9唔搭8"},{"pid":"6c39e9dfe127f9d69322096bc338efe40d495421","tid":2409712,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"記得條撚樣上年支持上飛機要比健康碼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}